comment: Warren (PHX) makes incidental contact with Wiggins (MIN) that does not affect his SQBR.
Bledsoe (PHX) makes incidental contact with Wiggins (MIN) that does not affect his SQBR.
Booker (PHX) does not release the ball prior to moving his pivot foot.
Dieng (MIN) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Chandler (PHX) sets the screen on Rubio (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The contact following the screen is marginal.
Towns (MIN) makes contact with Bledsoe's (PHX) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Rubio (MIN) gathers the ball with his left foot on the floor and then takes a legal two steps with his right foot and then left foot.
Chandler (PHX) sets the screen on Rubio (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LaVine (MIN) and Booker (PHX) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Chandler (PHX) makes contact with Wiggins' (MIN) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Chandler (PHX) sets the screen on Rubio (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Towns (MIN) makes contact to the body of Tucker (PHX) that affects his shot attempt.
Tucker (PHX) maintains legal guarding position on Wiggins (MIN) and the contact is incidental.
Tucker (PHX) legally contests Wiggins' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Wiggins (MIN) released his field goal attempt prior to the game clock expiring is confirmed.
